33:T82d,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"What does the Body Fat Calculator | Health actually measure?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"BMI measures the ratio of weight to height squared. It is a population-level screening tool, not a clinical measurement of body fat or health. A BMI in the normal range (18.5–24.9) is associated with lower statistical health risk, but individual health depends on many factors BMI does not capture."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Why can BMI be misleading for muscular people?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Muscle weighs more than fat per unit of volume. A highly trained athlete may have a BMI in the overweight range despite having very low body fat and excellent metabolic health. Conversely, an untrained person with \"normal\" BMI may carry excess body fat at a low weight."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What is the healthy BMI range for adults?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"The World Health Organization defines Underweight as BMI < 18.5, Normal as 18.5–24.9, Overweight as 25–29.9, and Obese as ≥ 30. Some health organizations use slightly adjusted cutoffs for specific ethnic groups, particularly for Asian populations where health risks appear at lower BMI values."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How much weight loss changes my BMI category?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"BMI decreases by approximately 1 unit for every 2.9 kg (6.4 lbs) of weight lost for someone 175 cm (5'9\") tall. For a 5'5\" person, the same BMI change requires about 2.4 kg. Use the calculator to enter a target weight and see what BMI it corresponds to."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Should children use the same BMI calculator as adults?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"No. BMI for children and adolescents (ages 2–19) is interpreted differently using age- and sex-specific growth charts. Pediatric BMI percentiles — not the adult thresholds — determine whether a child's weight is healthy. This calculator is designed for adults only."}}]}2a:["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$33"}}]
